Drosophila Home      ABSTRACTS: Assignments Lookup

Please click on the first letter of the presenting author's last name to view the assignment for either an oral or poster presentation. It is not possible to view abstract assignments using co-author names.  Poster Preview presentations are new this year and each person given a two-minute Poster Preview assignment will also have a poster presentation.

Student and postdoc GSA members: amplify your work and seek expert feedback by inviting specific scientists to attend your poster presentation via this request form.

If you have any questions or comments, please contact sbrown@genetics-gsa.org.

The Genetics Society of America (GSA) is an international professional membership organization for scientific researchers and educators in the field of genetics. We are dedicated to promoting genetics research and to facilitating communication among geneticists worldwide.
